help:set vertsize;help:set selvertsize;help:set edgesize
                        edgesize  (real number)

                   The size of edges.


                        vertsize (real number)

                 The size of vertices.


                      selvertsize (real number)

            The size of the selected vertex.
The scale depends on it, even if no vertex is selected.


          edgesize <= vertsize <= selvertsize
